# 📝 Resume Builder Form

A clean and minimal HTML form for collecting resume information, built with simplicity in mind.

## 🚀 Features
- All essential resume fields (Personal info, education, experience, skills)
- Clean Inter font for modern typography
- Responsive design works on all devices
- Simple validation for required fields
- PDF upload for resumes
- Profile photo upload support

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3 (with Inter font from Google Fonts)
- Basic form validation

## 📋 Form Fields

### Personal Information
- Full Name (required)
- Email (required)
- Phone (required)
- Date of Birth
- Gender
- Marital Status
- Nationality
- Address

### Professional Profiles
- LinkedIn URL
- GitHub URL

### Documents
- Profile Photo upload
- Resume PDF upload (required)

### Career Information
- Career Objective
- Highest Qualification (required)
- College/University (required)
- Year of Graduation (required)

### Skills & Experience
- Technical Skills
- Programming Languages
- Certifications
- Work Experience (years)
- Last Company
- Job Role

### Additional Info
- Languages Known
- Hobbies

### Declaration
- Accuracy confirmation checkbox (required)

## 🎨 Design Choices
- Uses Inter font family for clean, modern typography
- Simple, intuitive layout
- Blue submit button for clear call-to-action
- Required fields clearly marked
- Mobile-friendly responsive design

## 🔧 How to Use
1. Clone or download this repository
2. Open `index.html` in any web browser
3. Fill out the form
4. Submit (note: this is frontend only - backend integration would be needed for actual submission handling)

